lyrics.line: [Intro]
Fresh Boy Chilling
Sometimes you don't think you deserve something but
At times, it's what is given that you deserve
[Verse 1]
I'm a fighter, damn, I'm a fighter
I wanna fight for it, I wanna knock a man down for it
Let someone know how far I'll go for it
Maybe spin my heart, just to make a show for it
Kill or die, freeze a vibe
Make her know what I will do for it
This feeling engulfing, it's for it
How she's got me so meshed up, willy here
Emotions I can't take home
Just gotta let you know by these brawls
It's for you
My dose of your medicine will help me stay alive
Stayed alive for another day
Just wanna be with you girl through these days
With these heart parts
Flotsam on your waters
Sheen put back on
When you tell me just how much you could get on
When you're far, it's the dark
When the light comes on, you mess me up
And set me harder
I never thought it'd be that way
Never saying bye
Hi, a must I leave with that
Having you this close just to say
Code, Dakota is now on another chapter
We could see what comes after
